snippet.title: Johnny Depp REACTS to Amber Heard not being in JAIL yet
snippet.description:
The legal battle between Amber Heard and Johnny Depp continues. Even after officially being sentenced to jail for 4 years, Heard is still free! How does Depp feel about this? Find out on What’s Poppin’

Hollywood has been going crazy over Amber Heard and Johnny Depp’s legal battle. Watch our other video on WHY Zach Snyder must fire Amber Heard from Aquaman 2:
https://youtu.be/3z93fGxz8ww
